    "voice": [
      {
        "description": "np0267_carrier_monolog_1",
        "category": "event",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "おお……初めての場所なのになんだか懐かしい！不思議な感じがするね！",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E6%A1%83%E4%BA%95/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0267_carrier_monolog_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "np0267_carrier_monolog_2",
        "category": "event",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "やっぱここってすごいね……！",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E6%A1%83%E4%BA%95/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0267_carrier_monolog_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "np0267_carrier_monolog_3",
        "category": "event",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "本当、一時はどうなることかと思ったよー……。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E6%A1%83%E4%BA%95/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0267_carrier_monolog_3.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "np0267_carrier_monolog_4",
        "category": "event",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "持ってきたゲーム、全部クリアしちゃったぁ……。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E6%A1%83%E4%BA%95/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0267_carrier_monolog_4.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "np0267_carrier_monolog_5",
        "category": "event",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "これ、全部夢だったりして？",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E6%A1%83%E4%BA%95/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0267_carrier_monolog_5.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "np0267_carrier_select_1",
        "category": "event",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "こんなことだったらもっとゲーム持ってきたのに～！",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E6%A1%83%E4%BA%95/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0267_carrier_select_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "np0267_carrier_select_2",
        "category": "event",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "でもまぁ、前よりはスケールが小さいかも？",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E6%A1%83%E4%BA%95/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0267_carrier_select_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "np0267_carrier_select_3",
        "category": "event",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "でもちゃんと頑張ったよ！えへん！",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E6%A1%83%E4%BA%95/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0267_carrier_select_3.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "np0267_carrier_select_4",
        "category": "event",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "先生、カートリッジとか持ってない？",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E6%A1%83%E4%BA%95/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0267_carrier_select_4.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "np0267_carrier_select_5",
        "category": "event",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "現実が詰みゲーだよぉ……。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E6%A1%83%E4%BA%95/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0267_carrier_select_5.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "np0267_eventlobby_1",
        "category": "event",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "先輩たちの言う通りにやってみてるけど……！",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E6%A1%83%E4%BA%95/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0267_eventlobby_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "np0267_eventlobby_2",
        "category": "event",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "わぁ……ボタンとかなんかよく分からないものがいっぱい……。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E6%A1%83%E4%BA%95/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0267_eventlobby_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "np0267_eventlobby_3",
        "category": "event",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "アリス……ケイ……エイミ……トキ……会長……先生……。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E6%A1%83%E4%BA%95/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0267_eventlobby_3.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "np0267_eventlobby_4",
        "category": "event",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "せめて……せめて私が笑顔でいないとだよね！",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E6%A1%83%E4%BA%95/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0267_eventlobby_4.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "np0267_eventlobby_5",
        "category": "event",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "私たち勝てるよね先生？信じてるからねっ！",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E6%A1%83%E4%BA%95/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0267_eventlobby_5.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "np0267_eventlogin_1",
        "category": "event",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "一つ分かったことがあるよ！なーんにも分からないってこと！",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E6%A1%83%E4%BA%95/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0267_eventlogin_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "np0267_eventlogin_2",
        "category": "event",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "先生もやってみる？え、やらない？そっか……",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E6%A1%83%E4%BA%95/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0267_eventlogin_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "np0267_eventlogin_3",
        "category": "event",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "ラストスパートだよ、先生！いくよ！",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E6%A1%83%E4%BA%95/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0267_eventlogin_3.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "np0267_eventlogin_4",
        "category": "event",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "ヒマリ先輩に連れられて戻ってきたのはいいけど……。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E6%A1%83%E4%BA%95/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0267_eventlogin_4.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "np0267_eventlogin_5",
        "category": "event",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "（先生は無事なんだよね？大丈夫だよね……？）",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E6%A1%83%E4%BA%95/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0267_eventlogin_5.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "np0267_eventlogin_6",
        "category": "event",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "これで全部 終わらせよう！ ３人のためにも！",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E6%A1%83%E4%BA%95/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0267_eventlogin_6.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "np0267_eventlogin_7",
        "category": "event",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "今回は言えるかな……！来た、見た！勝っ……！てはないか……まだね。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E6%A1%83%E4%BA%95/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0267_eventlogin_7.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "np0267_r89_mainscenario_battle_7",
        "category": "battle",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "い、今のなにっ！？",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%8D%E7%BE%BD%20%E6%A1%83%E4%BA%95/%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%98/jp/np0267_r89_mainscenario_battle_7.ogg"
